snippet.textDisplay: Too much reverb and echos give it a film music mix effect. Coke Studio Pakistan is only different in that regard it has a studio feel. I think the whole magic is in Rohail Hayatt's Mixes. This and almost all other coke studio india's music ventures sounds pretty much like any of their shows Sa Re Ga Ma Pa or Surkeshtra. What is missing is a studio feel. People are sick of this sort of music. I think one should slap the mixing guy and let the music be as it is, without all that Reverbs and echos.
snippet.textOriginal: Too much reverb and echos give it a film music mix effect. Coke Studio Pakistan is only different in that regard it has a studio feel.
